title: Duo bot looking for group
body:
Duo bot smurfs looking for group to play with as we level accounts to 30, promise to pull our own weight, just get me out of the hell that is either

-Countless bots on my team
-countless bots on enemy team
-People either smurfing or using scripts
-People abusing shit like JG YI and using it against bad players, so by the time you see yi, he has 20 kills by 10 minutes.
